<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.8.3">
<l>aṇṭar kōṉeṉ ṉāṉai yeṉṟu māyar mātar koṅkai pulku</l>
<l>ceṇṭa ṉeṉṟum nāṉma ṟaikaḷ tēṭi yōṭuñ celva ṉeṉṟum</l>
<l>vaṇṭu lavupo ḻilkoḷ nāṅkai maṉṉu māya ṉeṉṟeṉ ṟōti</l>
<l>paṇṭu pōlaṉ ṟeṉma ṭantai pārttaṉ paḷḷi pāṭu vāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying, “King of heaven, my elephant,” saying, “He with a horsewhip</l>
<l rend="indent">whom the herdess’s breasts embraced,”</l>
<l>Saying, “Noble who hastened, seeking the four Vedas,”</l>
<l>Reciting over and over, “Māyaṉ who dwells in Nāṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">with groves where bees stir,”</l>
<l>[She] is not like before; my simple girl sings of Pārttaṉpaḷḷi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
